        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The scheme &quot;Pradhan Mantri Matasya Sampada Yojana: Provision of Polythene lining for the Construction of New ponds for Saline/Alkaline Area&quot; by the Ministry Of Fisheries, Animal Husbandry &amp; Dairying, Government of India, aims to provide central assistance for the cost of polythene lining for the construction of new ponds in saline or alkaline areas. Through this scheme, polythene lining costs are provided for new water bodies created under various state government initiatives. The intended beneficiaries are those creating new ponds for fish or shrimp culture in saline/alkaline areas. The scheme is implemented by the Fisheries Department, Government of Haryana.\n<br>\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n- The project cost is ₹8,00,000/- per hectare. \n- The subsidy provided will be limited to 25% of the project cost for all categories.\n\n<br>\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "The scheme aims to provide central assistance for the cost of polythene lining for new ponds in saline/alkaline areas. Through this scheme, polythene lining costs are provided to beneficiaries constructing new water bodies for fish/shrimp culture.",
        "exclusions_md": "",
        "detailedDescription": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The scheme \"Pradhan Mantri Matasya Sampada Yojana: Provision of Polythene lining for the Construction of New ponds for Saline/Alkaline Area\" by the Ministry Of Fisheries, Animal Husbandry & Dairying, Government of India, aims to provide central assistance for the cost of polythene lining for the construction of new ponds in saline or alkaline areas. Through this scheme, polythene lining costs are provided for new water bodies created under various state government initiatives. The intended beneficiaries are those creating new ponds for fish or shrimp culture in saline/alkaline areas. The scheme is implemented by the Fisheries Department, Government of Haryana."
              }
            ]
          },
